snippet.title: PIOZILA 2 - GYROSCOPIC CONTROL
snippet.description:
Control the character by rotating the device.

Piozila 2 is available for free on Google Play and App Store.

You can also control by touching the screen with your finger or saying words (left, right, ...).

Google play : https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.menamenagames.piozila2

App store : https://apps.apple.com/us/app/piozila-2/id6450461710

More information on https://menamenagames.com
